class="card card-featured"><h1 class="card-title">
Single-Page Website Examples - 5 Low-Maintenance Sites That Drive Conversion</h1><div
class="card-body"><div
class="card-text card-text-prebyline">In-depth reviews of 5 websites that champion simple navigation, a great mobile UX, and visual appeal on a single page.</div><div
class="card-byline"><div
class="card-byline-image">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/caro-profile-800x800-2024058.webp?crop=1:1,smart&width=80&dpr=2"
width="80"
height="80"
alt="Carolin Hewitt"
/></div><div
class="card-byline-details">
<span>By <a
class="card-byline-author" href="https://www.notzarla.com/contributors/carolin-hewitt">Carolin Hewitt</a>,</span>
<span
class="card-byline-date">Jul 24, 2024</span><div
class="card-byline-bio">
Carolin is a Copywriter for Zarla. She has a background in marketing communication and brand building, and has written articles about branding and logo design for small businesses.</div></div></div></div><div
class="card-image-holder"><div
class="card-preview">
