http://beautywithintuition.com
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Los Angeles, California, U.S.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Beauty with Intuition, founded by licensed cosmetologist Love Cordero, offers specialized Russian Classic lash extensions and training for lash artists in Los Angeles. The website features service details, a gallery of transformations, and a selection of recommended products available through an Amazon storefront.</p><p>The single-page website champions subtle elegance with a combination of a sleek serif typeface similar to those popular with luxury fashion brands, well-composed, concise, and relevant content, a gentle color palette, and a clean, well-spaced layout.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
