</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>A clearly marked floating anchor menu makes it easy to navigate up to different sections of the desktop site. The site's images are high-quality, and it features client testimonials, providing the business with credibility and building trust with potential clients.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
